{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":823,"text":"There we were,"},{"time":3354,"text":"souls and bodies packed\ninto a Texas church"},{"time":7428,"text":"on the last night of our lives."},{"time":10856,"text":"Packed into a room just like this,"},{"time":13542,"text":"but with creaky wooden pews\ndraped in worn-down red fabric,"},{"time":19287,"text":"with an organ to my left\nand a choir at my back"},{"time":21982,"text":"and a baptism pool\nbuilt into the wall behind them."},{"time":25502,"text":"A room like this, nonetheless."},{"time":29356,"text":"With the same great feelings of suspense,"},{"time":33080,"text":"the same deep hopes for salvation,"},{"time":36743,"text":"the same sweat in the palms"},{"time":38403,"text":"and the same people\nin the back not paying attention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41918,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":44770,"text":"This was December 31, 1999,"},{"time":49033,"text":"the night of the Second Coming of Christ,"},{"time":52222,"text":"and the end of the world as I knew it."},{"time":56022,"text":"I had turned 12 that year"},{"time":57672,"text":"and had reached the age of accountability."},{"time":60742,"text":"And once I stopped complaining"},{"time":62566,"text":"about how unfair it was\nthat Jesus would return"},{"time":65041,"text":"as soon as I had to be accountable\nfor all that I had done,"},{"time":68554,"text":"I figured I had better get\nmy house in order very quickly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72448,"text":"So I went to church as often as I could."},{"time":74415,"text":"I listened for silence as anxiously\nas one might listen for noise,"},{"time":79271,"text":"trying to be sure that the Lord\nhadn't pulled a fast one on me"},{"time":82385,"text":"and decided to come back early."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84813,"text":"And just in case he did,"},{"time":86988,"text":"I built a backup plan,"},{"time":89277,"text":"by reading the \"Left Behind\" books\nthat were all the rage at the time."},{"time":93651,"text":"And I found in their pages"},{"time":95139,"text":"that if I was not taken\nin the rapture at midnight,"},{"time":97904,"text":"I had another shot."},{"time":99958,"text":"All I had to do was avoid\ntaking the mark of the beast,"},{"time":103808,"text":"fight off demons, plagues\nand the Antichrist himself."},{"time":106944,"text":"It would be hard --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":108155,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":111348,"text":"but I knew I could do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":112930,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":114457,"text":"But planning time was over now."},{"time":116269,"text":"It was 11:50pm."},{"time":118109,"text":"We had 10 minutes left,"},{"time":119295,"text":"and my pastor called us\nout of the pews and down to the altar"},{"time":122313,"text":"because he wanted to be praying\nwhen midnight struck."},{"time":127808,"text":"So every faction of the congregation"},{"time":129842,"text":"took its place."},{"time":131169,"text":"The choir stayed in the choir stand,"},{"time":132939,"text":"the deacons and their wives --"},{"time":134436,"text":"or the Baptist Bourgeoisie\nas I like to call them --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":136963,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":138273,"text":"took first position in front of the altar."},{"time":140504,"text":"You see, in America,"},{"time":142824,"text":"even the Second Coming of Christ\nhas a VIP section."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145909,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":148263,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":153187,"text":"And right behind the Baptist Bourgeoisie"},{"time":155600,"text":"were the elderly --"},{"time":157553,"text":"these men and women whose young backs\nhad been bent under hot suns"},{"time":162465,"text":"in the cotton fields of East Texas,"},{"time":165137,"text":"and whose skin seemed to be burnt\na creaseless noble brown,"},{"time":168877,"text":"just like the clay of East Texas,"},{"time":171119,"text":"and whose hopes and dreams\nfor what life might become"},{"time":173628,"text":"outside of East Texas"},{"time":174803,"text":"had sometimes been bent and broken"},{"time":176470,"text":"even further than their backs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177993,"text":"Yes, these men and women\nwere the stars of the show for me."},{"time":182742,"text":"They had waited their whole lives\nfor this moment,"},{"time":185104,"text":"just as their medieval predecessors\nhad longed for the end of the world,"},{"time":189900,"text":"and just as my grandmother\nwaited for the Oprah Winfrey Show"},{"time":192921,"text":"to come on Channel 8\nevery day at 4 o'clock."},{"time":196242,"text":"And as she made her way to the altar,"},{"time":198215,"text":"I snuck right in behind her,"},{"time":200334,"text":"because I knew for sure"},{"time":202332,"text":"that my grandmother was going to heaven."},{"time":205126,"text":"And I thought that if I held on\nto her hand during this prayer,"},{"time":210282,"text":"I might go right on with her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":212976,"text":"So I held on"},{"time":214802,"text":"and I closed my eyes"},{"time":217070,"text":"to listen,"},{"time":218678,"text":"to wait."},{"time":220314,"text":"And the prayers got louder."},{"time":222428,"text":"And the shouts of response\nto the call of the prayer"},{"time":224893,"text":"went up higher even still."},{"time":226725,"text":"And the organ rolled on in\nto add the dirge."},{"time":229150,"text":"And the heat came on to add to the sweat."},{"time":231660,"text":"And my hand gripped firmer,"},{"time":233000,"text":"so I wouldn't be the one\nleft in the field."},{"time":235037,"text":"My eyes clenched tighter"},{"time":236260,"text":"so I wouldn't see the wheat\nbeing separated from the chaff."},{"time":239256,"text":"And then a voice rang out above us:"},{"time":242269,"text":"\"Amen.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":245474,"text":"It was over."},{"time":248044,"text":"I looked at the clock."},{"time":250643,"text":"It was after midnight."},{"time":253081,"text":"I looked at the elder believers"},{"time":255697,"text":"whose savior had not come,"},{"time":258205,"text":"who were too proud to show\nany signs of disappointment,"},{"time":261046,"text":"who had believed too much and for too long"},{"time":263972,"text":"to start doubting now."},{"time":267029,"text":"But I was upset on their behalf."},{"time":270650,"text":"They had been duped,"},{"time":272363,"text":"hoodwinked, bamboozled,"},{"time":273896,"text":"and I had gone right along with them."},{"time":276659,"text":"I had prayed their prayers,"},{"time":278054,"text":"I had yielded not to temptation\nas best I could."},{"time":281024,"text":"I had dipped my head not once, but twice"},{"time":284074,"text":"in that snot-inducing baptism pool."},{"time":286463,"text":"I had believed."},{"time":289355,"text":"Now what?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":291706,"text":"I got home just in time\nto turn on the television"},{"time":294845,"text":"and watch Peter Jennings\nannounce the new millennium"},{"time":297313,"text":"as it rolled in around the world."},{"time":299475,"text":"It struck me that it would have\nbeen strange anyway,"},{"time":303865,"text":"for Jesus to come back again and again"},{"time":306269,"text":"based on the different time zones."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307929,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":315037,"text":"And this made me feel\neven more ridiculous --"},{"time":318354,"text":"hurt, really."},{"time":321076,"text":"But there on that night,\nI did not stop believing."},{"time":325197,"text":"I just believed a new thing:"},{"time":327487,"text":"that it was possible not to believe."},{"time":330894,"text":"It was possible the answers\nI had were wrong,"},{"time":333330,"text":"that the questions themselves were wrong."},{"time":335701,"text":"And now, where there was once\na mountain of certitude,"},{"time":339772,"text":"there was, running right down\nto its foundation,"},{"time":343168,"text":"a spring of doubt,"},{"time":345691,"text":"a spring that promised rivers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":348357,"text":"I can trace the whole drama of my life"},{"time":351514,"text":"back to that night in that church"},{"time":353164,"text":"when my savior did not come for me;"},{"time":356069,"text":"when the thing I believed most certainly"},{"time":359328,"text":"turned out to be, if not a lie,"},{"time":361841,"text":"then not quite the truth."},{"time":364355,"text":"And even though most of you\nprepared for Y2K in a very different way,"},{"time":368937,"text":"I'm convinced that you are here"},{"time":371346,"text":"because some part of you has done\nthe same thing that I have done"},{"time":375278,"text":"since the dawn of this new century,"},{"time":378014,"text":"since my mother left\nand my father stayed away"},{"time":380484,"text":"and my Lord refused to come."},{"time":382867,"text":"And I held out my hand,"},{"time":384378,"text":"reaching for something to believe in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388587,"text":"I held on when I arrived at Yale at 18,"},{"time":392318,"text":"with the faith that my journey\nfrom Oak Cliff, Texas"},{"time":394856,"text":"was a chance to leave behind\nall the challenges I had known,"},{"time":398569,"text":"the broken dreams\nand broken bodies I had seen."},{"time":402542,"text":"But when I found myself back home\none winter break,"},{"time":407133,"text":"with my face planted in the floor,"},{"time":410268,"text":"my hands tied behind my back"},{"time":413538,"text":"and a burglar's gun pressed to my head,"},{"time":415536,"text":"I knew that even the best education\ncouldn't save me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420181,"text":"I held on when I showed up\nat Lehman Brothers"},{"time":423317,"text":"as an intern in 2008."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427048,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":431739,"text":"So hopeful --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":433078,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":436364,"text":"that I called home to inform my family"},{"time":438407,"text":"that we'd never be poor again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":439981,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":442767,"text":"But as I witnessed this temple of finance"},{"time":444825,"text":"come crashing down before my eyes,"},{"time":446664,"text":"I knew that even the best job\ncouldn't save me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":450599,"text":"I held on when I showed up\nin Washington DC as a young staffer,"},{"time":456476,"text":"who had heard a voice\ncall out from Illinois,"},{"time":458725,"text":"saying, \"It's been a long time coming,"},{"time":461621,"text":"but in this election, change\nhas come to America.\""},{"time":466549,"text":"But as the Congress ground to a halt"},{"time":468315,"text":"and the country ripped at the seams"},{"time":470057,"text":"and hope and change\nbegan to feel like a cruel joke,"},{"time":472514,"text":"I knew that even\nthe political second coming"},{"time":475845,"text":"could not save me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":477856,"text":"I had knelt faithfully at the altar\nof the American Dream,"},{"time":482340,"text":"praying to the gods of my time"},{"time":485261,"text":"of success,"},{"time":486834,"text":"and money,"},{"time":488358,"text":"and power."},{"time":490211,"text":"But over and over again,"},{"time":492619,"text":"midnight struck, and I opened my eyes"},{"time":495686,"text":"to see that all of these gods were dead."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499447,"text":"And from that graveyard,"},{"time":500852,"text":"I began the search once more,"},{"time":502321,"text":"not because I was brave,"},{"time":503615,"text":"but because I knew\nthat I would either believe"},{"time":507044,"text":"or I would die."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508963,"text":"So I took a pilgrimage\nto yet another mecca,"},{"time":512409,"text":"Harvard Business School --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":513779,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":516307,"text":"this time, knowing that I could not\nsimply accept the salvation"},{"time":520216,"text":"that it claimed to offer."},{"time":521470,"text":"No, I knew there'd be more work to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524981,"text":"The work began in the dark corner\nof a crowded party,"},{"time":530138,"text":"in the late night of an early,\nmiserable Cambridge winter,"},{"time":534457,"text":"when three friends and I asked a question"},{"time":536517,"text":"that young folks searching\nfor something real have asked"},{"time":539191,"text":"for a very long time:"},{"time":540982,"text":"\"What if we took a road trip?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":542680,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":546299,"text":"We didn't know where'd we go\nor how we'd get there,"},{"time":548753,"text":"but we knew we had to do it."},{"time":551108,"text":"Because all our lives we yearned,\nas Jack Kerouac wrote,"},{"time":554148,"text":"to \"sneak out into the night\nand disappear somewhere,\""},{"time":558991,"text":"and go find out what everybody was doing"},{"time":561068,"text":"all over the country."},{"time":563242,"text":"So even though there were\nother voices who said"},{"time":565543,"text":"that the risk was too great\nand the proof too thin,"},{"time":568020,"text":"we went on anyhow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570354,"text":"We went on 8,000 miles across America\nin the summer of 2013,"},{"time":576358,"text":"through the cow pastures of Montana,\nthrough the desolation of Detroit,"},{"time":579822,"text":"through the swamps of New Orleans,"},{"time":581469,"text":"where we found and worked\nwith men and women"},{"time":584095,"text":"who were building small businesses"},{"time":585804,"text":"that made purpose their bottom line."},{"time":589962,"text":"And having been trained\nat the West Point of capitalism,"},{"time":592672,"text":"this struck us as a revolutionary idea."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594800,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":595840,"text":"And this idea spread,"},{"time":598412,"text":"growing into a nonprofit\ncalled MBAs Across America,"},{"time":602820,"text":"a movement that landed me here\non this stage today."},{"time":607620,"text":"It spread because we found\na great hunger in our generation"},{"time":611821,"text":"for purpose, for meaning."},{"time":615317,"text":"It spread because we found\ncountless entrepreneurs"},{"time":618039,"text":"in the nooks and crannies of America"},{"time":619971,"text":"who were creating jobs and changing lives"},{"time":622448,"text":"and who needed a little help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":625082,"text":"But if I'm being honest, it also spread"},{"time":628392,"text":"because I fought to spread it."},{"time":631204,"text":"There was no length\nto which I would not go"},{"time":633471,"text":"to preach this gospel,"},{"time":634651,"text":"to get more people to believe"},{"time":637511,"text":"that we could bind the wounds\nof a broken country,"},{"time":639934,"text":"one social business at a time."},{"time":643116,"text":"But it was this journey of evangelism"},{"time":647239,"text":"that led me to the rather different gospel"},{"time":650136,"text":"that I've come to share with you today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":653867,"text":"It began one evening almost a year ago"},{"time":658199,"text":"at the Museum of Natural History\nin New York City,"},{"time":662371,"text":"at a gala for alumni\nof Harvard Business School."},{"time":666341,"text":"Under a full-size replica of a whale,"},{"time":669573,"text":"I sat with the titans of our time"},{"time":671948,"text":"as they celebrated their peers\nand their good deeds."},{"time":675727,"text":"There was pride in a room"},{"time":677035,"text":"where net worth\nand assets under management"},{"time":679938,"text":"surpassed half a trillion dollars."},{"time":683196,"text":"We looked over all that we had made,"},{"time":685863,"text":"and it was good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":687927,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":690868,"text":"But it just so happened,"},{"time":692959,"text":"two days later,"},{"time":694610,"text":"I had to travel up the road to Harlem,"},{"time":697455,"text":"where I found myself\nsitting in an urban farm"},{"time":699918,"text":"that had once been a vacant lot,"},{"time":702416,"text":"listening to a man named Tony\ntell me of the kids"},{"time":705340,"text":"that showed up there every day."},{"time":707944,"text":"All of them lived below the poverty line."},{"time":712075,"text":"Many of them carried\nall of their belongings in a backpack"},{"time":715519,"text":"to avoid losing them\nin a homeless shelter."},{"time":718432,"text":"Some of them came to Tony's program,"},{"time":721704,"text":"called Harlem Grown,"},{"time":723677,"text":"to get the only meal they had each day."},{"time":727465,"text":"Tony told me that he started Harlem Grown\nwith money from his pension,"},{"time":732954,"text":"after 20 years as a cab driver."},{"time":736232,"text":"He told me that he didn't give\nhimself a salary,"},{"time":739342,"text":"because despite success,\nthe program struggled for resources."},{"time":743993,"text":"He told me that he would take any help"},{"time":746665,"text":"that he could get."},{"time":748490,"text":"And I was there as that help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":752863,"text":"But as I left Tony,\nI felt the sting and salt of tears"},{"time":757838,"text":"welling up in my eyes."},{"time":760509,"text":"I felt the weight of revelation"},{"time":763187,"text":"that I could sit in one room on one night,"},{"time":767206,"text":"where a few hundred people\nhad half a trillion dollars,"},{"time":772187,"text":"and another room, two days later,"},{"time":774820,"text":"just 50 blocks up the road,"},{"time":777971,"text":"where a man was going without a salary"},{"time":780897,"text":"to get a child her only meal of the day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":784887,"text":"And it wasn't the glaring inequality\nthat made me want to cry,"},{"time":788441,"text":"it wasn't the thought of hungry,\nhomeless kids,"},{"time":791276,"text":"it wasn't rage toward the one percent"},{"time":793136,"text":"or pity toward the 99."},{"time":795787,"text":"No, I was disturbed\nbecause I had finally realized"},{"time":800330,"text":"that I was the dialysis"},{"time":802623,"text":"for a country that needed\na kidney transplant."},{"time":806647,"text":"I realized that my story\nstood in for all those"},{"time":810340,"text":"who were expected to pick\nthemselves up by their bootstraps,"},{"time":813206,"text":"even if they didn't have any boots;"},{"time":816182,"text":"that my organization stood in"},{"time":817879,"text":"for all the structural, systemic help\nthat never went to Harlem"},{"time":821653,"text":"or Appalachia or the Lower 9th Ward;"},{"time":823622,"text":"that my voice stood in\nfor all those voices"},{"time":829098,"text":"that seemed too unlearned,\ntoo unwashed, too unaccommodated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":835273,"text":"And the shame of that,"},{"time":837721,"text":"that shame washed over me"},{"time":839132,"text":"like the shame of sitting\nin front of the television,"},{"time":842898,"text":"watching Peter Jennings\nannounce the new millennium"},{"time":845421,"text":"again"},{"time":846653,"text":"and again"},{"time":848257,"text":"and again."},{"time":849796,"text":"I had been duped,"},{"time":852084,"text":"hoodwinked,"},{"time":853696,"text":"bamboozled."},{"time":855403,"text":"But this time, the false savior was me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":859600,"text":"You see, I've come a long way \nfrom that altar"},{"time":863326,"text":"on the night I thought\nthe world would end,"},{"time":866371,"text":"from a world where people spoke in tongues"},{"time":869107,"text":"and saw suffering\nas a necessary act of God"},{"time":872222,"text":"and took a text to be infallible truth."},{"time":874314,"text":"Yes, I've come so far"},{"time":876607,"text":"that I'm right back where I started."}]},{"cues":[{"time":880103,"text":"Because it simply is not true to say"},{"time":882342,"text":"that we live in an age of disbelief --"},{"time":884247,"text":"no, we believe today just as much\nas any time that came before."},{"time":889409,"text":"Some of us may believe\nin the prophecy of Bren√© Brown"},{"time":892276,"text":"or Tony Robbins."},{"time":894003,"text":"We may believe in the bible\nof The New Yorker"},{"time":896127,"text":"or the Harvard Business Review."},{"time":898146,"text":"We may believe most deeply"},{"time":900150,"text":"when we worship right here\nat the church of TED,"},{"time":903347,"text":"but we desperately want to believe,"},{"time":905552,"text":"we need to believe."},{"time":908001,"text":"We speak in the tongues\nof charismatic leaders"},{"time":910210,"text":"that promise to solve all our problems."},{"time":912426,"text":"We see suffering as a necessary act\nof the capitalism that is our god,"},{"time":916530,"text":"we take the text of technological progress"},{"time":919540,"text":"to be infallible truth."},{"time":922034,"text":"And we hardly realize\nthe human price we pay"},{"time":926412,"text":"when we fail to question one brick,"},{"time":929692,"text":"because we fear it might shake\nour whole foundation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":933677,"text":"But if you are disturbed"},{"time":936080,"text":"by the unconscionable things\nthat we have come to accept,"},{"time":939777,"text":"then it must be questioning time."},{"time":943987,"text":"So I have not a gospel\nof disruption or innovation"},{"time":948058,"text":"or a triple bottom line."},{"time":950380,"text":"I do not have a gospel of faith\nto share with you today, in fact."},{"time":955125,"text":"I have and I offer a gospel of doubt."},{"time":960000,"text":"The gospel of doubt does not ask\nthat you stop believing,"},{"time":963737,"text":"it asks that you believe a new thing:"},{"time":966200,"text":"that it is possible not to believe."},{"time":969512,"text":"It is possible the answers\nwe have are wrong,"},{"time":971706,"text":"it is possible the questions\nthemselves are wrong."},{"time":974313,"text":"Yes, the gospel of doubt means\nthat it is possible that we,"},{"time":978619,"text":"on this stage, in this room,"},{"time":981178,"text":"are wrong."},{"time":982779,"text":"Because it raises the question, \"Why?\""},{"time":985789,"text":"With all the power\nthat we hold in our hands,"},{"time":988988,"text":"why are people still suffering so bad?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":993209,"text":"This doubt leads me to share\nthat we are putting my organization,"},{"time":997788,"text":"MBAs Across America,"},{"time":999078,"text":"out of business."},{"time":1000730,"text":"We have shed our staff\nand closed our doors"},{"time":1003246,"text":"and we will share our model freely"},{"time":1005298,"text":"with anyone who sees\ntheir power to do this work"},{"time":1008208,"text":"without waiting for our permission."},{"time":1010434,"text":"This doubt compels me"},{"time":1013236,"text":"to renounce the role of savior"},{"time":1015033,"text":"that some have placed on me,"},{"time":1016901,"text":"because our time is too short\nand our odds are too long"},{"time":1020020,"text":"to wait for second comings,"},{"time":1021824,"text":"when the truth is that\nthere will be no miracles here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1026305,"text":"And this doubt, it fuels me,"},{"time":1028737,"text":"it gives me hope"},{"time":1030606,"text":"that when our troubles overwhelm us,"},{"time":1033760,"text":"when the paths laid out for us\nseem to lead to our demise,"},{"time":1038528,"text":"when our healers bring\nno comfort to our wounds,"},{"time":1042286,"text":"it will not be our blind faith --"},{"time":1045423,"text":"no, it will be our humble doubt"},{"time":1048730,"text":"that shines a little light\ninto the darkness of our lives"},{"time":1052065,"text":"and of our world"},{"time":1053870,"text":"and lets us raise our voice to whisper"},{"time":1056833,"text":"or to shout"},{"time":1058437,"text":"or to say simply,"},{"time":1060176,"text":"very simply,"},{"time":1061706,"text":"\"There must be another way.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1065011,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1066186,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}